[normal]&#xa0;[bold]S[bold]elect Committee on the European Union[bold]Sub-Committee B - Internal Market, Infrastructure and Employment[bold]Call for Evidence[bold] - EU Action to Tackle Youth Unemployment[bold]&#xa0;[bold]Response from Institute [bold]For[bold] Employment Studies (IES) by[bold]Kari P Hadjivassiliou and Stefan [bold]Speckesser[bold]&#xa0;[bold]1[bold]. 
[normal]Do you think that the EU should be providing funding to Member States to tackle youth unemployment? Does EU action respect Member States’ powers in the area of social and employment affairs?[bold] 
